From Points South:
	Take I-95 North to Exit 8. At the end of the ramp at the stoplight, make a left on Atlantic Street. Then, make a right at Tresser Boulevard. After the first stoplight on Tresser, make a right into the private road in front of the Marriott Hotel. The entrance to the parking garage for One Stamford Plaza will be on your left, directly in front of the Marriott's main entrance. You will see visitor parking reserved on Level 1 in the garage. Please remember to bring your parking ticket to reception for validation.

	Take Merritt Parkway (U.S. Route 15) North to Exit 34. At the end of the ramp, turn right onto Connecticut Route 104 South (Long Ridge Road). Make a right onto Cold Spring Road. Continue onto Washington Boulevard for 1.5 miles. Turn left at Tresser Boulevard. After passing through Atlantic Street and Greylock Place, make a right into the private road in front of the Marriott Hotel. The entrance to the parking garage for One Stamford Plaza will be on your left, directly in front of the Marriott’s main entrance. You will see visitor parking reserved on Level 1 in the garage. Please remember to bring your parking ticket to reception for validation.

From Points North:
	Take I-95 South to Exit 8. At the end of the ramp at the stoplight, continue straight on North State Street, passing the four Stamford Plaza buildings on your right. Make a right on Marriott Road. At this point, the Marriott Hotel will be on your left, and One Stamford Plaza will be on your right. The entrance to the parking garage for One Stamford Plaza will be on your right, directly in front of the Marriott's main entrance. You will see visitor parking reserved on Level 1 in the garage. Please remember to bring your parking ticket to reception for validation.

	Take Merritt Parkway (U.S. Route 15) South to Exit 34. At the end of the ramp, turn left onto Connecticut Route 104 South (Long Ridge Road). Make a right onto Cold Spring Road. Continue onto Washington Boulevard for 1.5 miles. Turn left at Tresser Boulevard. After passing through Atlantic Street and Greylock Place, make a right into the private road in front of the Marriott Hotel. The entrance to the parking garage for One Stamford Plaza will be on your left, directly in front of the Marriott’s main entrance. You will see visitor parking reserved on Level 1 in the garage. Please remember to bring your parking ticket to reception for validation.









